original: Llndell, Carl Alfred Waldemar, landsfiskal, Söderköping, f. 1/12/82 i Örebro av fabr. Alfred L. o. Sofia Charlotta Nilsson. — Genomg. h. allm. lärov., kronolänsm :ex. 05, genomg. kriminaltekn. kursen v. Sthlms liögsk. s. statsstip. 30. Kont:skriv, å kronolänsm rkont. 02, e. o. lands-kansi. i Gävleb. 1. 05, landskansl. där 07, kronolänsm. i Skärkinds härad, Ös-tergötl. 1., 12, landsfiskal i Skärkinds distr. sed. 18, tjg. ss. stadsfiskal i Gävle o. Söderköp. Kronoomb. v. kronouppbördsstämmor o. i tax:ndr, ordf. i tax :nd, omb :man o. kassör v. sparbank 03-05. Sv. vägfören. dipl. 19, KAK plak. 27, Sv. motorcykelkl. silverplak. 32.
translated: Llndell, Carl Alfred Waldemar, district magistrate, Söderköping, b. 1/12/82 in Örebro, son of factory worker Alfred L. and Sofia Charlotta Nilsson. - Attended upper secondary school, completed district court examiner training in 1905, completed criminal technology course at Stockholm University with a state scholarship in 1930. Employment: clerk at the district court in 1902, assistant district chancellor in Gävle county in 1905, district chancellor in Gävle county in 1907, district magistrate in Skärkinds district, Östergötland county, in 1912, district magistrate in Skärkinds district since 1918, served as municipal prosecutor in Gävle and Söderköping, an official at the county council meetings for tax collection and tax assessment, chairman of the tax board, delegate and treasurer at the savings bank from 1903 to 1905. Received diploma from the Swedish Road Association in 1919, awarded plaque by the Swedish Automobile Club (KAK) in 1927, received silver plaque from the Swedish Motorcycle Club in 1932.
